      "instruction": "<p>Once the sweet potato is tender, add the <strong>soft cheese</strong>, <strong>shredded spring greens </strong>and <strong>half </strong>of the <strong>chopped basil </strong>to the pan (save the rest for later!)</p><p>Cook, covered, for a final 3 min or until the spring greens are tender – this is your<strong> creamy ribollita stew</strong></p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> if needed</p>",
